Google Fonts Similar to Bebas Neue\"</span></a> &#8594;</p><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-bebas-neue/\">Google Fonts Similar to Bebas Neue</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"arthur\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3961:\"<p>Bebas Neue is an open-source font designed by Ryoichi Tsunekawa and released under his company <a href=\"https://dharmatype.com\">Dharma Type</a>. It features a single weight (regular) and is an all-caps font.</p><p>Prior to Bebas Neue, Ryoichi released a font named &#8216;Bebas&#8217;. In 2010 Bebas was re-designed and released as Bebas Neue. Both the original and the Neue version were both released with a license that allows the fonts to be used for free, both in personal and commercial applications.</p><p>Bebas Neue is an extremely popular font and has been downloaded over ten million times. In 2019 Ryoichi released a premium version named &#8216;Bebas Neue Pro&#8217; which includes lowercase characters and five new weights.</p><p>Bebas Neue Pro is an extremely high quality font which does not come cheap. A web license will set you back around $150 per 10,000 page views.</p><h2>Google Fonts Alternatives</h2><p>There is an <a href=\"https://github.com/google/fonts/issues/1192\">active thread</a> requesting the inclusion of Bebas Neue in the Google Fonts library that has support from Ryoichi himself. That may one day become a reality, until then here is three similar fonts we found.</p><h3>Oswald Medium</h3><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-oswald-medium.jpg\" alt=\"Oswald Comparison with Bebas Neue\" class=\"wp-image-2718\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-oswald-medium.jpg 1280w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-oswald-medium-300x92.jpg 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-oswald-medium-768x235.jpg 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-oswald-medium-1024x314.jpg 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-oswald-medium-640x196.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /><figcaption>Oswald Comparison</figcaption></figure><h3>Roboto Condensed</h3><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-roboto-condensed.jpg\" alt=\"Roboto Condensed Comparison with Bebas Neue\" class=\"wp-image-2717\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-roboto-condensed.jpg 1280w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-roboto-condensed-300x92.jpg 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-roboto-condensed-768x235.jpg 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-roboto-condensed-1024x314.jpg 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-roboto-condensed-640x196.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /><figcaption>Roboto Condensed Comparison</figcaption></figure><h3>Cabin Condensed</h3><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-cabin-condensed.jpg\" alt=\"Cabin Condensed Comparison with Bebas Neue\" class=\"wp-image-2716\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-cabin-condensed.jpg 1280w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-cabin-condensed-300x92.jpg 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-cabin-condensed-768x235.jpg 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-cabin-condensed-1024x314.jpg 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/bebas-neue-alternative-cabin-condensed-640x196.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /><figcaption>Cabin Condensed Comparison</figcaption></figure><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-bebas-neue/\">Google Fonts Similar to Bebas Neue</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-bebas-neue/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"          \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"Top 10 Fun Fonts (Free &amp; Premium)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://fontsplugin.com/free-fun-fonts/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"https://fontsplugin.com/free-fun-fonts/#respond\