8217;s important to check the licensing terms. Almost every font is free to use for personal and non-profit use. However, only some are free for commercial use too.</p><h4>1) <a href=\"https://www.1001fonts.com/mistervampire-font.html\">Mister Vampire</a></h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/mister-vampire-font-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2685\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/mister-vampire-font-1024x512.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/mister-vampire-font-300x150.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/mister-vampire-font-768x384.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/mister-vampire-font-640x320.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/mister-vampire-font.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure><h4>2) <a href=\"https://www.1001fonts.com/zhang-qa-font.html\">Zhang QA</a></h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/zhang-qa-font-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2686\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/zhang-qa-font-1024x512.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/zhang-qa-font-300x150.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/zhang-qa-font-768x384.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/zhang-qa-font-640x320.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/zhang-qa-font.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure><h4>3) <a href=\"https://www.1001fonts.com/chocolate-bar-demo-font.html\">Chocolate Bar Font</a></h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/chocolate-bar-font-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2687\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/chocolate-bar-font-1024x512.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/chocolate-bar-font-300x150.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/chocolate-bar-font-768x384.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/chocolate-bar-font-640x320.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/chocolate-bar-font.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure><h4>4) <a href=\"https://www.1001fonts.com/a-little-sunshine-font.html\">A little sunshine</a></h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/a-little-sunshine-font-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2688\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/a-little-sunshine-font-1024x512.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/a-little-sunshine-font-300x150.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/a-little-sunshine-font-768x384.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/a-little-sunshine-font-640x320.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/a-little-sunshine-font.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure><h4>5) <a href=\"https://www.fontspace.com/des/cookiemonster\">Cookie Monster</a></h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"611\" src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/cookiemonster-font-letters-charmap-35667-1024x611.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2689\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/cookiemonster-font-letters-charmap-35667-1024x611.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/cookiemonster-font-letters-charmap-35667-300x179.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/cookiemonster-font-letters-charmap-35667-768x458.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/cookiemonster-font-letters-charmap-35667-640x382.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/cookiemonster-font-letters-charmap-35667.png 1173w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure><p></p><h2>Premium Fu